data.value: How to play: 1.) The host will create a lobby for the players to join into. The host will also pick which category/categories they want for the games' questions. 2.) Each player can pick out their names and character. 3.) Once the lobby is set, we can start the match. Each player will be given a question to answer, If a player gets it right they'll get a point and will be safe for the round, whoever gets the wrong answer will not get a point. 4.) It's a race to rack up 15 points. Good luck!
